{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449590/extras/description0_1.gif?t=1730280513\" /><br>Leonardo's Island is an adventure/building game set in the age of pirates, featuring wooden constructions and sailboats. <br>You left the comfort of your parents' house in search of adventure, treasure, and freedom. But now, you find yourself alone on the island as pirates approach. It\u2019s time to take action!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449590/extras/building.png?t=1730280513\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449590/extras/resources1.gif?t=1730280513\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449590/extras/building1.gif?t=1730280513\" /><br><br>Create your new home, design your flag, hang a hammock, and relax! <br>Build structures to complete the campaign, dive for cannons, and protect the island!<br><br>You can build your own ships with 1, 2, or 5 sails \u2014 the design is entirely up to you!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449590/extras/boatbuilding1.gif?t=1730280513\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449590/extras/battles.png?t=1730280513\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449590/extras/battles1.gif?t=1730280513\" /><br><br>Fortification is key in defending against pirates.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449590/extras/earlyaccesss.png?t=1730280513\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449590/extras/earlyaccess1.gif?t=1730280513\" /><br><br>I have been developing this game for 8 years. <br>My dream is to incorporate all the ideas that I couldn't include in the early access version of the game. <br>Many thanks to William, the composer whom I was very fortunate to meet.","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1449590?t=1730280513","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449590/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1730280513","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449590/6253f4a2deabd01cdf68fddf70019089d662856e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730280513","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449590/6253f4a2deabd01cdf68fddf70019089d662856e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1730280513","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3162710,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449590/extras/description0_1.gif?t=1730280513\" /><br>Leonardo's Island is an adventure/building game set in the age of pirates, featuring wooden constructions and sailboats. <br>You left the comfort of your parents' house in search of adventure, treasure, and freedom. But now, you find yourself alone on the island as pirates approach. It\u2019s time to take action!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449590/extras/building.png?t=1730280513\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449590/extras/resources1.gif?t=1730280513\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449590/extras/building1.gif?t=1730280513\" /><br><br>Create your new home, design your flag, hang a hammock, and relax! <br>Build structures